OL,3,CBritish farmers say 'shocking' levels
OL,4,Cof floods are pushing them to the brink
OL,6,FBy , ITV News Multimedia Producer
OL,8,F"I know in this area who are really
OL,9,Fstruggling at this moment just because
OL,10,Fthey do not know what to do," says
OL,11,FPeter Gardiner, a Norfolk-based farmer.
OL,13,F"Eighty percent of my grazing marshes
OL,14,Fwith cattle on went under water in
OL,15,Fprobably a six or seven day period.
OL,16,FMost of the arable land didn't flood,
OL,17,Fbut was too wet to do anything with."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/16
