OL,3,CBritish farmers say 'shocking' levels
OL,4,Cof floods are pushing them to the brink
OL,6,FMr Gardiner told ITV News some of his
OL,7,Fland has been flooded since last
OL,8,FOctober, adding that, while farmers
OL,9,Fare used to dealing with wet weather,
OL,10,Fthere has been "shocking" levels of
OL,11,Frainfall over autumn and winter.
OL,13,FHis story is one that thousands of
OL,14,Ffarmers are currently describing
OL,15,Facross the UK, where acres upon acres
OL,16,Fof land, usually set aside for arable
OL,17,Ffarming, have been submerged under
OL,18,Fwater - in some places up to three
OL,19,Fmetres deep.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/16
