OL,6,FThe - only one short of the record
OL,7,F(11) set in 2015-16 when the Met
OL,8,FOffice first started naming storms.
OL,10,FThese storms - such as October's Storm
OL,11,FBabet and Henk in January - combined
OL,12,Fwith periods of intense rainfall have
OL,13,Fdecimated farmland and left some
OL,14,Ffarmers concerned they might miss out
OL,15,Fon an entire cropping season.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/16
