OL,3,CBritish farmers say 'shocking' levels
OL,4,Cof floods are pushing them to the brink
OL,6,FData from the UK Centre for Ecology
OL,7,Fand Hydrology (UKCEH) showed that soil
OL,8,Fmoisture levels - or how saturated the
OL,9,Fground was - at the majority of sites
OL,10,Fit monitors were high or above
OL,11,Fcapacity in its two most recent
OL,12,Fmonthly reports (January 2024 and
OL,13,FDecember 2023).
OL,15,FThis was despite rainfall in January
OL,16,Fbeing "close to average" because
OL,17,Fprevious months of heavy rain meant
OL,18,Fthat the ground had not been given an
OL,19,Fopportunity to dry out.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/16
