OL,6,FThe Met Office, meanwhile, said that
OL,7,Falthough , it was also the wettest for
OL,8,Fsome parts of the former - including
OL,9,FEast Anglia which saw 106.4mm of
OL,10,Frainfall across the month .
OL,12,F"As farmers we are dictated by the
OL,13,Fweather, our whole business revolves
OL,14,Faround the weather," Mr Gardiner said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/16
