OL,3,CBritish farmers say 'shocking' levels
OL,4,Cof floods are pushing them to the brink
OL,6,FThe National Farmers' Union (NFU) has
OL,7,Fblamed cuts to the Environment
OL,8,FAgency's (EA) annual flood defence
OL,9,Fmaintenance budget as to why the
OL,10,Fimpacts of flooding have become more
OL,11,Fpronounced in recent years.
OL,13,FNFU Flooding Policy Adviser Zoe Moore
OL,14,Fcited a report from the National Audit
OL,15,FOffice (NAO), which found a #34
OL,16,Fmillion deficit in the EA's budget for
OL,17,F2022-23.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/16
