OL,3,CBritish farmers say 'shocking' levels
OL,4,Cof floods are pushing them to the brink
OL,6,FShe said farmers could be left facing
OL,7,Fa "really difficult financial
OL,8,Fdecision" as early as next autumn if
OL,9,Fflooding continues at the current rate.
OL,11,FLast month, the NFU's outgoing
OL,12,Fpresident Minette Batters told the
OL,13,Forganisation's annual conference that
OL,14,Fextreme weather, such as flooding, was
OL,15,Fone of a number of challenges facing
OL,16,Ffarmers.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/16
