OL,3,CBritish farmers say 'shocking' levels
OL,4,Cof floods are pushing them to the brink
OL,6,FHer successor, Tom Bradshaw, has since
OL,7,Furged the government to deliver extra
OL,8,Fsupport for farmers, saying in a
OL,9,Fletter to Chancellor Jeremy Hunt it is
OL,10,F"vital that our country's food
OL,11,Fproducers have the business confidence
OL,12,Fto continue producing climate-
OL,13,Ffriendly, nutritious food long-term".
OL,15,FHe implored ministers to maintain
OL,16,Fexisting flood defences to be able to
OL,17,F"better accommodate regular extreme
OL,18,Frainfall events and allow for swifter
OL,19,Frecovery from flooding on agricultural
OL,20,Fland".
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/16
