OL,6,FThe government has said some farmers,
OL,7,Fdepending on their eligibility, could
OL,8,Fbe in line to receive up to #25,000 in
OL,9,Fsupport grants after the severe
OL,10,Fweather brought about by Storms Babet
OL,11,Fand Henk, but application windows for
OL,12,Fthis have yet to open.
