OL,3,CBritish farmers say 'shocking' levels
OL,4,Cof floods are pushing them to the brink
OL,6,FThe prospect of reduced yields for
OL,7,FBritish farmers has raised some
OL,8,Fconcerns about potential knock-on
OL,9,Fimpacts for consumers at the
OL,10,Fsupermarket.
OL,12,FDavid Eudall, Director of Economics
OL,13,Fand Analysis at the Agricultural and
OL,14,FHorticulture Development Board (AHDB),
OL,15,Ftold ITV News a similar weather
OL,16,Fpattern in the autumn and winter of
OL,17,F2019-20 led to a 24% reduction in the
OL,18,Fplanted area for the harvest of 2020.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/16
