OL,3,CBritish farmers say 'shocking' levels
OL,4,Cof floods are pushing them to the brink
OL,6,FHe added the AHDB is expecting
OL,7,F"something of a similar magnitude"
OL,8,Fwhen farmers come to harvest their
OL,9,Fcrops later this year.
OL,11,FBut the British Retail Consortium
OL,12,F(BRC) has moved to reassure consumers
OL,13,Fthat any impacts to product
OL,14,Favailability or pricing will be
OL,15,Flimited.
OL,17,F"Supply chains are under pressure from
OL,18,Fa variety of reasons including extreme
OL,19,Fweather conditions," Andrew Opie,
OL,20,FDirector of Food and Sustainability at
OL,21,Fthe BRC, said in a statement.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G12/16
