OL,4,Cof floods are pushing them to the brink
OL,6,F"Despite these challenges, retailers
OL,7,Fhave continued to deliver excellent
OL,8,Fservice for their customers and are
OL,9,Fworking hard to limit price increases."
OL,11,FIn the face of extreme weather, some
OL,12,Ffarmers are now turning to agri-
OL,13,Fenvironmental schemes to guarantee a
OL,14,Fsource of income from their land, Ms
OL,15,FMoore said.
OL,17,FThe move is something that Mr Gardiner
OL,18,Fsays he is already employing, planting
OL,19,Fso-called 'energy crops' - such as
OL,20,Fmaize - to diversify his harvest.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G13/16
