OL,3,CBritish farmers say 'shocking' levels
OL,4,Cof floods are pushing them to the brink
OL,6,FBut he warned that not every farmer
OL,7,Fwill necessarily be in a position to
OL,8,Ffollow suit.
OL,10,F"A lot of land will be taken out of
OL,11,Fproduction this year or out of food
OL,12,Fproduction and either go into energy
OL,13,Fcrops, agri-environment schemes or
OL,14,Fjust be left bear because either
OL,15,Ffarmers are not prepared to take the
OL,16,Frisk and lose more money or they just
OL,17,Fphysically cannot do anything with the
OL,18,Fland."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G14/16
