OL,3,CBritish farmers say 'shocking' levels
OL,4,Cof floods are pushing them to the brink
OL,6,FHe added that, even with changes to
OL,7,Ffarming practices, were current levels
OL,8,Fof flooding to become a yearly
OL,9,Foccurrence it would force many
OL,10,Ffarmers, including himself, to
OL,11,Fconsider their long-term future.
OL,13,F"You run a business, that's the
OL,14,Fquestion I have to ask myself: 'How do
OL,15,FI run a beef herd with the uncertainty
OL,16,Fof every year or every other year I
OL,17,Fmay have this problem?'. That's a
OL,18,Fproblem that business would not be
OL,19,Fable to withstand over a long period
OL,20,Fof time."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G15/16
